    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Trade blankets made for the Hudson's Bay Company, of various weights and colors, often patterned with broad weft bands and points.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
